{
  "texts": [
    "All cultures have their roots in agriculture.",
    "The agricultural sector employs approximately one billion individuals worldwide, which accounts for approximately 28% of the employed population (Anon.2018a).",
    "India, China and United States are the major cultivators globally, having the highest net cropped area (Anon. 2018b).",
    "Every aspect of crop cultivation must be considered to ensure a higher yield throughout the year.",
    "A global agricultural harvest is expected to be lost by 10-16% annually due to plant diseases, costing USD 220 billion."
  ]
}